values:
I had the best time with kristina and allison last night!
We took tons of pictures so Ill put them up here later.

I seriously miss allison. I've been having the time of my life lately. Im finding out that the more I change for the better, the more people dont like me. Theres a boy who doesnt like me just because Im religious. It was weird hearing that, seeing as it was the first time ive ever heard anything like that.
Im waiting in breathless anticipation for sunday, thats when I find out if my special gal gets to live with me. = ) Im excited, if its a no, I will honestly be crushed.
Christmas is coming soon and I cant wait actually..usually I hate christmas but I cant wait for this one...you know?
I dont know whats up with me lately but Ive been crying and puking and Ive just been sad lately. I have no reason to, I just do.
Allison and I have known each other our whole lives and Im glad shes still my friend. In all honesty she makes me rediculously happy.
Someone told me I was beautiful last night and it struck me speechless. I was the most honest thing Ive ever heard, I want to marry this boy. But I cant. Hes been spoken for. Tim is still in texas...I sent out christmas cards last night and wrote my uncle a letter...as gay as it sounds , i like that were pen pals. I mean he lives in alaska, and I get to visit there soon, whos comin with me?!..
I desperately need a new layout, who wants to do it for me.
I saw kristina C. today and everytime i see her, her beauty just ..glows. I ever realised how gorgeous she was till she puller her hair our of her face, her style now does her justice and shes just amazingly pretty. Im kinda jealous I cant pull it off.
I went shopping all weekend and week, Ive spent about 250-500 bucks...somewhere in there.
I want hello kitty stuff for christmas, but there so many hello kitty styles, I like the origninal and the ballerina, I dont likw when she has her bunny friend, thats too japanese for me. =P
I hung out with olivia and that was fun, we talkeda lot. I dont think she likes me tho.
I get to work with hillary all week..

gotta go bye!

My phone is completely fucked up and I can only recieve calls and I cant see who they are.
Im beginning to hate Nokia.
This sucks ass, Im going to get a new phone soon.

This is my last entry because I dont think its neccisary to have everyone in my biz nass. 
Fuck Livejournal.
Im outie 2000
= )
